BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 362.00 Tm (- Need per-row logic? Row-level.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 348.00 Tm (- Need SUM/AVG level in current view? Aggregate.) Tj ET
