BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 586.00 Tm (- Histogram: distribution of one measure.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 572.00 Tm (- Box plot: distribution and outliers.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 558.00 Tm (- Maps: geographic analysis.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 544.00 Tm (- Heat map/highlight table: intensity across categories.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 530.00 Tm (- Bullet chart: actual vs target.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 516.00 Tm (- Gantt chart: duration/timeline.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 502.00 Tm (- Waterfall chart: positive/negative contribution to total.) Tj ET
