BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 371.00 Tm (- "How are values distributed?" Use histogram or box plot.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 357.00 Tm (- "How are two measures related?" Use scatter plot.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 343.00 Tm (- "What is current vs target?" Use bullet chart or bar-in-bar.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 329.00 Tm (- "What makes up the total?" Use stacked bar, treemap, or limited pie/donut.) Tj ET
