BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 296.00 Tm (- Sort bars when comparing.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 282.00 Tm (- Use labels only where helpful.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 268.00 Tm (- Avoid too many colors.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 254.00 Tm (- Use consistent colors for same meanings.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 240.00 Tm (- Do not use pie charts with too many slices.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 226.00 Tm (- Always match chart type to the business question.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 54.00 207.00 Tm ([TAKEAWAY] = Summary: Good chart selection starts from the question, not from what looks fancy.) Tj ET
