BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 352.00 Tm (- Do not rush into building charts without a plan.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 338.00 Tm (- Translate every requirement into a chart or dashboard element.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 324.00 Tm (- Use one consistent mockup/design for related dashboards.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 310.00 Tm (- Reuse structure when making a second dashboard.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 296.00 Tm (- Test calculations in simple tables before relying on them in visuals.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 282.00 Tm (- Test filters, parameters, actions, and navigation.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 54.00 263.00 Tm ([TAKEAWAY] = Summary: Real Tableau work is structured. Requirements drive chart choices, chart) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 54.00 249.00 Tm (choices drive layout, and testing protects correctness.) Tj ET
