BT /F2 18 Tf 0.05 0.12 0.20 rg 1 0 0 1 54.00 784.00 Tm (Answer Key) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 750.00 Tm (1. Business Intelligence: paggamit ng data analysis at reporting para makagawa ng better) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 736.00 Tm (decisions.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 722.00 Tm (2. Raw data ay hilaw at mahirap intindihin; insight ay meaningful understanding/actionable) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 708.00 Tm (finding mula sa data.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 694.00 Tm (3. Volume, Velocity, Variety.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 680.00 Tm (4. Kapag kailangan ng automation, large data handling, security, centralized sharing, at) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 666.00 Tm (interactive dashboards.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 652.00 Tm (5. Desktop is paid/professional/private authoring tool; Public is free but intended for) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 638.00 Tm (public publishing/learning.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 624.00 Tm (6. Live queries source directly for freshness; extract uses copied optimized data for) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 610.00 Tm (performance.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 596.00 Tm (7. Packaged workbook containing workbook plus data/assets.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 582.00 Tm (8. It converts user interactions into queries and renders visualizations.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 568.00 Tm (9. Logical layer uses relationships and keeps tables separate; physical layer uses) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 554.00 Tm (joins/unions and can merge tables.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 540.00 Tm (10. Join adds columns side by side; union stacks rows vertically.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 526.00 Tm (11. Relationships are flexible and reduce risk of duplicate/lost rows compared with joins.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 512.00 Tm (12. When combining different data sources at worksheet/visualization level.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 498.00 Tm (13. Dimension is grouping/category field, e.g. Category, Country, Customer Name.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 484.00 Tm (14. Measure is numeric field for calculation, e.g. Sales, Profit, Quantity.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 470.00 Tm (15. Discrete creates separate headers/categories; continuous creates axis/range.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 456.00 Tm (16. Alias changes displayed value names, e.g. DE shown as Germany.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 442.00 Tm (17. Hierarchy creates drill-down levels like Country > City > Postal Code.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 428.00 Tm (18. Group is manual grouping of members; set is subset membership that can be) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 414.00 Tm (dynamic/condition-based.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 400.00 Tm (19. Chart showing distribution of values across bins.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 386.00 Tm (20. Because filters happen at different stages and can affect results/performance) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 372.00 Tm (differently.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 358.00 Tm (21. User-controlled variable value used in calculations, filters, reference lines, titles,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 344.00 Tm (etc.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 330.00 Tm (22. Parameter must be connected to a calculation/filter/reference line/etc. to affect the) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 316.00 Tm (view.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 302.00 Tm (23. Interaction triggered by user action, such as filter, highlight, URL, navigation, set,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 288.00 Tm (or parameter action.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 274.00 Tm (24. Row-level, aggregate, table calculation, and LOD expression.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 260.00 Tm (25. When calculation must stay at a specified granularity regardless of current view.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 246.00 Tm (26. They handle null values; IFNULL replaces null, ZN converts null numeric values to zero.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 232.00 Tm (27. Line chart.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 218.00 Tm (28. Histogram or box plot.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 204.00 Tm (29. Containers organize layout, alignment, spacing, and structure.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 0 0 0 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 190.00 Tm (30. Requirements define what questions to answer, which charts to build, and how the) Tj ET
